trans-unit.source: Holds the list of items that constitute the content of an <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Innehåller listan över objekt som utgör innehållet i en <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: ItemCollection maintains a collection of items such as strings, objects, [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xml](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-xml-md.md)] nodes, elements, and other collections.
trans-unit.target: ItemCollection upprätthåller en samling objekt, till exempel strängar, objekt, [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xml](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-xml-md.md)] noder, element och andra samlingar.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl> uses the data in the ItemCollection to generate its content.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl>använder data i ItemCollection för att generera dess innehåll.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl>

trans-unit.source: If you want to aggregate more than one collection, assign a <xref:System.Windows.Data.CompositeCollection> to the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.ItemsSource%2A> property of your <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl>.
trans-unit.target: Om du vill att sammanställa flera samlingar, tilldela en <xref:System.Windows.Data.CompositeCollection> <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.ItemsSource%2A>egenskap i <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.ItemsSource%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Data.CompositeCollection>

trans-unit.source: Use either the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.Items%2A> property or the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.ItemsSource%2A> property to specify the collection that should be used to generate the content of your <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl>.
trans-unit.target: Använd antingen <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.Items%2A>egenskapen eller <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.ItemsSource%2A>att ange den samling som ska användas för att generera innehåll i din <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.ItemsSource%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.Items%2A>

trans-unit.source: When the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.ItemsSource%2A> property is set, the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.Items%2A> collection will be made read-only and fixed-size.
trans-unit.target: När den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.ItemsSource%2A>egenskap är inställd på <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.Items%2A>samlingen kommer att göras skrivskyddade och fast storlek.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.Items%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.ItemsSource%2A>

trans-unit.source: This means that if you are using the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.ItemsSource%2A> property, you cannot add, delete, or change items in the ItemCollection directly.
trans-unit.target: Detta innebär att om du använder den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.ItemsSource%2A>egenskapen som du kan inte lägga till, ta bort eller ändra objekt i ItemCollection direkt.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.ItemsSource%2A>

trans-unit.source: ItemCollection is a <xref:System.Windows.Data.CollectionView> and therefore provides collection view functionalities, such as sorting, grouping, and filtering.
trans-unit.target: ItemCollection är en <xref:System.Windows.Data.CollectionView>och ger därför samling visa överallt, till exempel sortering, gruppering och filtrering.</xref:System.Windows.Data.CollectionView>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemCollection.SortDescriptions%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemCollection.Filter%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemCollection.GroupDescriptions%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Mer information finns i <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemCollection.SortDescriptions%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemCollection.Filter%2A>, och <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemCollection.GroupDescriptions%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemCollection.GroupDescriptions%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemCollection.Filter%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemCollection.SortDescriptions%2A>
